snippet.title: Exclusive LudoNarraCon Trailer - Two new Patrons visit Tavern Talk!
snippet.description:
We are so proud to be a part of the LudoNarraCon and have something special prepared for you! The last two new patrons that are visiting Tavern Talk and the Wayfarer's Inn!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2076140/Tavern_Talk/

Check out LudoNarraCon: https://www.ludonarracon.com/

Directed by Tommaso Crogliano
Script by Tommaso Crogliano, Selima Heiser & Jasmin Düsterloh
Animation & Art by Nika Gorev & Clara Furtwängler
Edit by Tommaso Crogliano
Musik by Filippo Beck Peccoz: www.fbpsound.com 

Our Voice Actors:
Sarah Nightingale as the tavern owner: https://www.nightingale-voices.com/sarah
